    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>import java.util.Date;   \nDate now = new Date();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note that the <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/Date.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Date</a> object is mutable and if you want to do anything sophisticated, use <a href=\"http://joda-time.sourceforge.net/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">jodatime</a>.</p>\n"
